# E2E tests

If a test is testing for 0-downtime operations, no transient failures are allowed for that test.
Do not twist it around.

Use "make test-e2e GINKGO_FOCUS..." to run specific tests, do not call ginkgo directly.

E2E tests are not deploying the operator in the cluster but they run it in-process.

Wait maximum 15 seconds in loops or when performing a kubectl operation.
Prefer using a small script that checks every few seconds in a loop and exits when test is done running.
